# M7 Design System Manifest — what to ignore vs commit when consuming this skill
# in another project:
#   - Commit: .design-master/design-system.json (the locked source of truth)
#   - Ignore: .design-master/exports/ and .design-master/pages/ (regenerable)
#
# In THIS repo (the skill itself), nothing in .design-master/ should be created.
# But just in case, ignore the regenerable subdirs:
.design-master/exports/
.design-master/pages/
